# ChangeLog for mail-mta/postfix
# Copyright 1999-2011 Gentoo Foundation; Distributed under the GPL v2
# $Header: /var/cvsroot/gentoo-x86/mail-mta/postfix/ChangeLog,v 1.233 2011/02/28 00:00:18 radhermit Exp $

*postfix-2.8.1 (28 Feb 2011)

  28 Feb 2011; Tim Harder <radhermit@gentoo.org> +postfix-2.8.1.ebuild:
  Version bump. Update vda patch, add doc and examples USE flags to selectively
  install optional files, use mysql_config to get the mysql linking libraries,
  don't install legacy sendmail symlink, remove unnecessary config files, and
  don't install a new main.cf config file if one already exists (fixes bug
  #349944).

  29 Jan 2011; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> postfix-2.7.2.ebuild:
  alpha/arm/ia64/s390/sh/sparc stable wrt #352654

  26 Jan 2011; Pawel Hajdan jr <phajdan.jr@gentoo.org> postfix-2.7.2.ebuild:
  x86 stable wrt bug #352654

  25 Jan 2011; Markos Chandras <hwoarang@gentoo.org> postfix-2.7.2.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64 wrt bug #352654

  25 Jan 2011; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> postfix-2.7.2.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #352654).

*postfix-2.8.0-r1 (24 Jan 2011)

  24 Jan 2011; Tim Harder <radhermit@gentoo.org> -postfix-2.8.0.ebuild,
  +postfix-2.8.0-r1.ebuild:
  Revbump to add sqlite USE flag (bug #352405 by Andreis_Vinogradovs) and
  remove old.

  22 Jan 2011; Kacper Kowalik <xarthisius@gentoo.org> postfix-2.7.1.ebuild:
  ppc/ppc64 stable wrt #343313

*postfix-2.8.0 (21 Jan 2011)

  21 Jan 2011; Tim Harder <radhermit@gentoo.org> -postfix-2.8.0_rc3.ebuild,
  +postfix-2.8.0.ebuild:
  Version bump and remove old.

*postfix-2.8.0_rc3 (19 Jan 2011)

  19 Jan 2011; Tim Harder <radhermit@gentoo.org> -postfix-2.8.0_rc2.ebuild,
  +postfix-2.8.0_rc3.ebuild:
  Version bump and remove old.

*postfix-2.8.0_rc2 (18 Jan 2011)

  18 Jan 2011; Tim Harder <radhermit@gentoo.org> -postfix-2.8.0_rc1.ebuild,
  +postfix-2.8.0_rc2.ebuild:
  Version bump and remove old.

*postfix-2.8.0_rc1 (18 Jan 2011)

  18 Jan 2011; Tim Harder <radhermit@gentoo.org> +postfix-2.8.0_rc1.ebuild:
  Version bump to the latest release candidate.

  04 Dec 2010; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> postfix-2.7.1.ebuild:
  alpha/ia64/s390/sh/sparc stable wrt #343313

*postfix-2.7.2 (27 Nov 2010)

  27 Nov 2010; Tim Harder <radhermit@gentoo.org> -postfix-2.7.1-r1.ebuild,
  +postfix-2.7.2.ebuild:
  Version bump (bug #346875 by Michael Orlitzky) and remove old. Remove
  unnecessary version restriction on net-mail/mailbase dependency, remove old
  warnings, use emake instead of make, and add warning for a potential
  compatibility problem on systems using certificate verification.

*postfix-2.7.1-r1 (07 Nov 2010)

  07 Nov 2010; Tim Harder <radhermit@gentoo.org> +postfix-2.7.1-r1.ebuild:
  Revision bump to update the VDA patch.

  05 Nov 2010; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> postfix-2.7.1.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #343313).

  04 Nov 2010; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> postfix-2.7.1.ebuild:
  arm stable, bug #343313

  03 Nov 2010; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> postfix-2.7.1.ebuild:
  x86 stable, bug #343313

  31 Oct 2010; Markos Chandras <hwoarang@gentoo.org> postfix-2.7.1.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64 wrt bug #343313

*postfix-2.7.1 (25 Sep 2010)

  25 Sep 2010; Tim Harder <radhermit@gentoo.org> +postfix-2.7.1.ebuild:
  Version bump (fixes bug #316577, thanks to Artur Frysiak for reporting),
  update to EAPI=3, remove old mailer-config setup, and remove old warnings
  relating to postfix versions not in the tree.

  06 Sep 2010; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> postfix-2.6.6.ebuild:
  Marking postfix-2.6.6 ppc64 for bug 320179

  27 Aug 2010; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> postfix-2.6.6.ebuild:
  ia64/s390/sh/sparc stable wrt #320179

  23 Jul 2010; Tobias Klausmann <klausman@gentoo.org> postfix-2.6.6.ebuild:
  Stable on alpha, bug #320179

  26 Jun 2010; <nixnut@gentoo.org> postfix-2.6.6.ebuild:
  ppc stable #320179

  24 Jun 2010; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> postfix-2.6.6.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #320179).

  20 Jun 2010; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> postfix-2.6.6.ebuild:
  arm/x86 stable, bug #320179

  17 Jun 2010; Patrick Lauer <patrick@gentoo.org> postfix-2.6.5.ebuild,
  postfix-2.6.6.ebuild, postfix-2.6.7.ebuild:
  Migrating away from deprecated postgres virtuals

  14 Jun 2010; Christoph Mende <angelos@gentoo.org> postfix-2.6.6.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64 wrt bug #320179

