  alpha/arm/ia64/s390/sh/sparc stable wrt #278343

  21 Jul 2009; <chainsaw@gentoo.org> postfix-2.5.7.ebuild:
  Mark stable on AMD64 as requested by Tobias Scherbaum
  <dertobi123@gentoo.org> in bug #277343. Tested on a dual dual-core Opteron
  2218 in combination with mail-filter/amavisd-new-2.6.1-r1.

  19 Jul 2009; nixnut <nixnut@gentoo.org> postfix-2.5.7.ebuild:
  ppc stable #277343

