  stable x86, bug 277343

  14 Jul 2009; Gordon Malm <gengor@gentoo.org> postfix-2.6.2-r1.ebuild:
  Add dropped change - Avoid gcc-version test under non-hardened, stylistic
  change wrt #76512.

